thread.title: Kristie Karima Burns
thread.title_full: Canvasdiscount reviewed by Kristie Karima Burns

author: Kristie Karima Burns
title: Kristie Karima Burns
text: For the price I paid I was willing to accept anything. I was just "testing the service" to see if it would actually work for me. I ended up being amazed. I ordered the largest canvas available and it actually arrived within one week, the quality was great and it arrived all assembled in a large box on my doorstep. I'm going to order more again today <3
